s defence of the Church against the State. Since the later Middle Ages <i>Hugh</i> has also been used as an Anglicized form of the Gaelic name Aodh ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs. Hugh MacDuff was born in 1109, in Wemyss, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom. She had at least 1 son with Hugh MacDuff. She died in her hometown."},"et":{"1109–":"1109–Surnud","1105–Male":"1105–Surnud","1135–1195":"1135–1195","1109–Female":"1109–Surnud","1105":"1105","1135":"1135","1195":"1195","1109":"1109","Coaltown of Wemyss, Fife, Scotland":"Wemyss, Fife, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Wemyss, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Wemyss, Fife, Šotimaa, United Kingdom","Fife, Scotland":"Fife, Scotland"},"fi":{"1109–":"1109–Kuollut","1105–Male":"1105–Kuollut","1135–1195":"1135–1195","1109–Female":"1109–Kuollut","1105":"1105","1135":"1135","1195":"1195","1109":"1109","Coaltown of Wemyss, Fife, Scotland":"Wemyss, Fife, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Wemyss, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Wemyss, Fife, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta","Fife, Scotland":"Fife, Scotland"},"fr":{"1109–":"1109–Décédée","1105–Male":"1105–Décédé","1135–1195":"1135–1195","1109–Female":"1109–Décédée","1105":"1105","1135":"1135","1195":"1195","1109":"1109","Coaltown of Wemyss, Fife, Scotland":"Wemyss, Fife, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Wemyss, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Wemyss, Fife, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","Fife, Scotland":"Fife, Écosse","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Hugh MacDuff est née en 1109, à Wemyss, Fife, Écosse, Royaume-Uni. Elle a eu au moins 1 fils avec Hugh MacDuff. Elle est décédée dans sa ville natale."},"de":{"1109–":"1109–Verstorben","1105–Male":"1105–Verstorben","1135–1195":"1135–1195","1109–Female":"1109–Verstorben","1105":"1105","1135":"1135","1195":"1195","1109":"1109","Coaltown of Wemyss, Fife, Scotland":"Wemyss, Fife, Schottland, United Kingdom","Wemyss, Fife, Scotland, United Kingdom":"Wemyss, Fife, Schottland, United Kingdom","Fife, Scotland":"Fife, Scotland","lifeSummary":"Mrs. Hugh MacDuff wurde 1